    "description": "MCX International Enterprises is actively seeking a talented and motivated Risk Analyst to join our dynamic team in Jabalpur. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout MCX International Enterprises:\nMCX International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with MCX International Enterprises!",
